e><br />\n<br />\n不過真係少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda776697c7d26768b72d39fa512e0479bfa4020","tid":41054,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"all back都順眼先叫靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e3a1d5b69f0c6f2fae79ee30f32e2c37abcff5","tid":41054,"uid":4901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgJ7DX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbgJ7DX8.jpg&h=987b2e28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/022043_0ba71a93103df4408d44fa2a6df7c230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F022043_0ba71a93103df4408d44fa2a6df7c230.jpg&h=a7c821a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fb40834e9f358b212261d0af60df24466bcff1b","tid":41054,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得all back 靚<br />\n但問番人先知好難整到咁靚 除非有髮型師</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點為之整得靚。翻學all back ok已經好唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣頭型髮線靚 髮量夠 唔太攣唔太粗太幼<br />\n紮又要有技巧要貼服 形狀pull得好睇 條辮唔dum落黎etc<br />\n<br />\n不過男性會理所當然以為求其向後一紮就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9ced4584ffa232ec15718eeaaa06cebd2c3777","tid":41054,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有幾個女仔朋友all back唔差<br />\n不過女仔9成都係鍾意有pat陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打中意邊type</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無咩指定邊type <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實遇到同明星model好難比較<br />\n基本上現實唔會鍾意好靚既人<br />\n但如果計出名既人就係袁澧林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：宜家對一個all back既女仔幾有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都鐘意咗樓下個惠康女仔，佢all back 又係好靚，特別對眼，同佢對望嗰陣真係有交流嘅感覺，就係因為呢樣留意咗佢好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打邊區？個女仔幾歲左右？<br />\n我都見過女仔做惠康係all back眼靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7e9f8f8cf7cdab270fbfad37e58b07c136d5fb","tid":41054,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:19:36.000Z","msg":"Btw d大陸妹好鍾意all back<br />\n但好多個額都成個壽星公咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611e387357bd65894a178c149b080ce5a3f92602","tid":41054,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5zt67p4c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5zt67p4c&h=b989e86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雪炫完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27e3c421abaa27e420a238df338b6328b7053ed","tid":41054,"uid":7004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:23:12.000Z","msg":"中分好睇既話all back係咪都應該一樣?<br />\n因為都係露全額<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab616ceec8a7daa09f8407b3b75e10123464393","tid":41054,"uid":53426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:25:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45246e47fb0924f4dcbf1b6386987127ce81c0bf","tid":41054,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sgav9fpq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsgav9fpq&h=483d0f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙津個額都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb110fd9f0